1. *Bomba* je eksplodirala u centru grada. (The bomb exploded in the city center.)
2. Policija je pronašla *bombu* u napuštenom stanu. (The police found a bomb in an abandoned apartment.)
3. *Bombama* su uništeni najvažniji objekti u gradu. (The most important buildings in the city were destroyed by bombs.)
4. *Bombardovanje* je prekinuto posle nekoliko sati. (The bombardment was stopped after several hours.)
5. Putnici su bili uskraćeni za let zbog *bombe* koja je pronađena na aerodromu. (The passengers were denied the flight due to the bomb that was found at the airport.)